<br>
If people actualy had to group for there low end exp (example soling warriors and clerics getting insane exp) then maybe those empty zones would get some use and any newbs to the game would have someone to learn something from.  I still remember the glory days my first wizard had in crushbone, I'd say I had some of the most fun in the game in that zone with my first character.<br>
<br>
